headline: Centene (CNC) Valuation Check As New Care Initiatives Expand Medicaid And Complex Care Reach
summary: Centene (CNC) has been active on the care delivery front, with subsidiaries expanding palliative care in Ohio through Tuesday Health and recognizing new Foster Care Centers of Excellence in Texas within its STAR Health Medicaid program. See our latest analysis for Centene. These care delivery moves arrive during a strong run in the shares, with a 30 day share price return of 15.54% and a 90 day share price return of 35.28%. However, the 1 year total shareholder return sits at a 28.63% loss,...
